message: Hello Bob, I am offering you my product for $115. I believe this price reflects its value while allowing us to reach an agreement.
Thanks for the offer, Alice. I'm interested, but I'm only willing to pay $105.  Let me know what you think.
Thank you for your interest, Bob. After considering your offer, I've decided to counter with a price of $110 for the product. I hope this meets within your budget.
